quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  41,26,Abo abaakafuwala nebagamba nti temuwuliriza Kur’ani eno wabula mujizannyiremu oba olyawo ne muwangula
  41,27,Ddala tugenda kukombya abo abaakafuwala ku bibonerezo ebikakali era tugenda kubasasulira ddala obubi bwebyo bye baalinga bakola
  41,28,"Ogwo omuliro yempeera ya balabe ba Katonda, balina mu gwo obutuulo obw'olubeerera nga eyo yempeera (gye balifuna) olwokubanga baawakanya ebigambo byaffe"
  41,29,"Abo abaakafuwala baligamba nti ayi Mukama omulabirizi waffe, tulage mu Majinni n’abantu abo abaatubuza tubasse wakati w'ebigere byaffe balyoke babe mu ba wansi (ddala)"
  41,30,"Mazima abo abagamba nti Katonda ye Mukama omulabirizi waffe oluvanyuma ne babeera beesimbu, ba Malayika bakka (nga bajja) gyebali (nga babagamba nti) temutya era temweraliikirira era musanyuke olw’ejjana eyo gye mwalinga mulagaanyisibwa"
  41,31,"Ffe (Ba Malayika) ffe banna mmwe mu bulamu obwensi ne mu bulamu obw'enkomerero, era mulina okufuna nga muli mu yo, ebyo emyooyo gya mmwe bye gyagala era nga bwe mulina okufuna ebyo bye musaba"
  41,32,(Ebyo) nga bugenyi obuva ewa (Katonda) omusonyiyi ennyo omusaasizi